102#ifdef DEBUG
103static size_t hash_collisions;
104#endif
105
106static char **license_hash[HASH_SIZE];
107static const char license_spaces[] = " \t\n";
108static const char license_chars[] =
109 "ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZabcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz0123456789_-.";
110
111static size_t
112hash_license(const char *license, size_t len)
113{
114 size_t hash;
115
116 for (hash = 0; *license && len; ++license, --len)
117 hash = *license + hash * 32;
118 return hash % HASH_SIZE;
119}
120
121static void
122add_license_internal(const char *license, size_t len)
123{
124 char *new_license;
125 size_t slot, i;
126
127 slot = hash_license(license, len);
128
129 new_license = malloc(len + 1);
130 memcpy(new_license, license, len);
131 new_license[len] = '\0';
132
133 if (license_hash[slot] == NULL) {
134 license_hash[slot] = calloc(sizeof(char *), 2);
135 license_hash[slot][0] = new_license;
136 } else {
137 for (i = 0; license_hash[slot][i]; ++i) {
138 if (!memcmp(license_hash[slot][i], license, len) &&
139 license_hash[slot][i][len] == '\0') {
140 free(new_license);
141 return;
142 }
143 }
144
145#ifdef DEBUG
146 ++hash_collisions;
147#endif
148
149 license_hash[slot] = realloc(license_hash[slot],
150 sizeof(char *) * (i + 2));
151 license_hash[slot][i] = new_license;
152 license_hash[slot][i + 1] = NULL;
153 }
154}
155
156int
157add_licenses(const char *line)
158{
159 const char *next;
160
161 if (line == NULL)
162 return 0;
163
164 for (line += strspn(line, license_spaces); line; ) {
165 next = line + strspn(line, license_chars);
166 if (next == line)
167 return *line ? -1 : 0;
168 add_license_internal(line, next - line);
169 line = next + strspn(next, license_spaces);
170 if (next == line)
171 return *line ? -1 : 0;
172 }
173 return 0;
174}
175
176static int
177acceptable_license_internal(const char *license, size_t len)
178{
179 size_t slot, i;
180
181 slot = hash_license(license, len);
182
183 if (license_hash[slot] == NULL)
184 return 0;
185
186 for (i = 0; license_hash[slot][i]; ++i) {
187 if (strncmp(license_hash[slot][i], license, len) == 0 &&
188 license_hash[slot][i][len] == '\0')
189 return 1;
190 }
191
192 return 0;
193}
194
195int
196acceptable_license(const char *license)
197{
198 size_t len;
199
200 len = strlen(license);
201 if (strspn(license, license_chars) != len) {
202 warnx("Invalid character in license name at position %" PRIzu, len);
203 return -1;
204 }
205
206 return acceptable_license_internal(license, len);
207}
208
209static int
210acceptable_pkg_license_internal(const char **licensep, int toplevel, const char *start)
211{
212 const char *license = *licensep;
213 int need_parenthesis, is_true = 0;
214 int expr_type = 0; /* 0: unset, 1: or, 2: and */
215 size_t len;
216
217 license += strspn(license, license_spaces);
218
219 if (*license == '(' && !toplevel) {
220 need_parenthesis = 1;
221 ++license;
222 license += strspn(license, license_spaces);
223 } else {
224 need_parenthesis = 0;
225 }
226
227 for (;;) {
228 if (*license == '(') {
229 switch (acceptable_pkg_license_internal(&license, 0, start)) {
230 case -1:
231 return -1;
232 case 0:
233 if (expr_type == 2)
234 is_true = 0;
235 break;
236 case 1:
237 is_true = 1;
238 break;
239 }
240 license += strspn(license, license_spaces);
241 } else {
242 len = strspn(license, license_chars);
243 if (len == 0) {
244 warnx("Invalid character in license name at position %" PRIzu, license - start + 1);
245 return -1;
246 }
247
248 if (acceptable_license_internal(license, len)) {
249 if (expr_type != 2)
250 is_true = 1;
251 } else if (expr_type == 2) {
252 is_true = 0;
253 }
254
255 license += len;
256
257 len = strspn(license, license_spaces);
258 if (len == 0 && *license && *license != ')') {
259 warnx("Missing space at position %" PRIzu, license - start + 1);
260 return -1;
261 }
262 license += len;
263 }
264
265 if (*license == ')') {
266 if (!need_parenthesis) {
267 warnx("Missing open parenthesis at position %" PRIzu, license - start + 1);
268 return -1;
269 }
270 *licensep = license + 1;
271 return is_true;
272 }
273 if (*license == '\0') {
274 if (need_parenthesis) {
275 warnx("Unbalanced parenthesis at position %" PRIzu, license - start + 1);
276 return -1;
277 }
278 *licensep = license;
279 return is_true;
280 }
281
282 if (strncmp(license, "AND", 3) == 0) {
283 if (expr_type == 1) {
284 warnx("Invalid operator in OR expression at position %" PRIzu, license - start + 1);
285 return -1;
286 }
287 expr_type = 2;
288 license += 3;
289 } else if (strncmp(license, "OR", 2) == 0) {
290 if (expr_type == 2) {
291 warnx("Invalid operator in AND expression at position %" PRIzu, license - start + 1);
292 return -1;
293 }
294 expr_type = 1;
295 license += 2;
296 } else {
297 warnx("Invalid operator at position %" PRIzu, license - start + 1);
298 return -1;
299 }
300 len = strspn(license, license_spaces);
301 if (len == 0 && *license != '(') {
302 warnx("Missing space at position %" PRIzu, license - start + 1);
303 return -1;
304 }
305 license += len;
306 }
307}
308
309int
310acceptable_pkg_license(const char *license)
311{
312 int ret;
313
314 ret = acceptable_pkg_license_internal(&license, 1, license);
315 if (ret == -1)
316 return -1;
317 license += strspn(license, license_spaces);
318 if (*license) {
319 warnx("Trailing garbage in license specification");
320 return -1;
321 }
322 return ret;
323}
324
325void
326load_license_lists(void)
327{
328 if (add_licenses(getenv("PKGSRC_ACCEPTABLE_LICENSES")))
329 errx(EXIT_FAILURE, "syntax error in PKGSRC_ACCEPTABLE_LICENSES");
330 if (add_licenses(acceptable_licenses))
331 errx(EXIT_FAILURE, "syntax error in ACCEPTABLE_LICENSES");
332 if (add_licenses(getenv("PKGSRC_DEFAULT_ACCEPTABLE_LICENSES")))
333 errx(EXIT_FAILURE, "syntax error in PKGSRC_DEFAULT_ACCEPTABLE_LICENSES");
334 if (add_licenses(default_acceptable_licenses))
335 errx(EXIT_FAILURE, "syntax error in DEFAULT_ACCEPTABLE_LICENSES");
336}
